headline: Targa Resources Corp. Prices $1.5 Billion Offering of Senior Notes
summary: HOUSTON, June 04, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Targa Resources Corp. headline: Equifax And 2 Companies That Might Be Trading Below Their Estimated Value
summary: The United States market has experienced a flat performance over the last week but has seen a 13% increase over the past year, with earnings forecasted to grow by 14% annually. In this environment, identifying stocks that may be trading below their estimated value can offer potential opportunities for investors seeking to capitalize on future growth prospects.
